data.description: Modern townhome in peaceful Bull Mountain with wonderful open floor plan. Kitchen designed for entertaining with quartz countertops, stainless appliances and island that looks into living room with sliding door to balcony. Dual primary bedrooms, primary #1 with walk in shower and closet organizer. Enphase Solar system, EV charging outlet, double car deep garage opens up to fenced back yard with covered cedar deck. HOA includes access to rec room, gym and swimming pool. Short walk to pet-friendly Roshak park with basketball hoop, play structures.
